{"tid":749702,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"唔係講笑 好多香港人連呼吸咁基本都唔識","createTime":"2018-07-20T08:56:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-21T03:32:42.000Z","uid":195396,"like":3,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a8ddf4d49c7aae4eefb12ecf117ba0ac14cba8e0","tid":749702,"uid":195396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T08:56:15.000Z","msg":"我就係其中之一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n早一兩年身體差左好多 個人慢落黎先發現自己好多野好似好簡單都做唔好<br />\n<br />\n例如 點樣放慢呼吸 以前個人一緊張呼吸就亂晒 又會自己閉左氣 慢慢靠自己意識提返自己呼吸<br />\n<br />\n又例如放鬆 禁得電話多 條頸長期處於用力狀態 學左好耐先識放鬆<br />\n<br />\n仲有行路 香港人平時行得快 時間耐左自己真係唔識放慢放鬆黎行<br />\n<br />\n其實講咁多 都係想取下暖 有無人同我一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有的話希望各位多d留意自己身體 唔好咁緊張操勞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e3803570a92127dcd253f00b5a8319550d1c8fa","tid":749702,"uid":194876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T08:58:36.000Z","msg":"我坐直企直都唔識"},{"pid":"3a886aac5b87f4c3a5f1875ef57a7792b970cae7","tid":749702,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T08:59:58.000Z","msg":"手動呼吸定自動呼吸"},{"pid":"b593d8ca83979057023c5032ebaac6a416906a5a","tid":749702,"uid":195396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e3803570a92127dcd253f00b5a8319550d1c8fa","tid":749702,"uid":194876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T08:58:36.000Z","msg":"我坐直企直都唔識"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T09:01:31.000Z","msg":"呢個又係<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係街等燈 入lift 企係度都要&quot;挨挨bungbung&quot; <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65fc7e08d15f03988dd11c26f48b592c4de41805","tid":749702,"uid":195396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a886aac5b87f4c3a5f1875ef57a7792b970cae7","tid":749702,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T08:59:58.000Z","msg":"手動呼吸定自動呼吸"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T09:04:33.000Z","msg":"認真呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我好集中做一樣野就會閉左氣自己都唔知<br />\n例如要扭d好細既縲絲 甚至斟水落個細樽蓋咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb7cb97ea40d282f19fd87fec70be813f888aa16","tid":749702,"uid":74262,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T09:05:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4407d29ce93db9a5550f9097b5a89f108c69771b","tid":749702,"uid":62373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T09:09:42.000Z","msg":"呢句真呀<br />\n呼吸閉左 自己都唔知<br />\n之後先慢慢提自己 先正常返"},{"pid":"202d1ac92a9a3e5e90617b85c7a57b2505cee88e","tid":749702,"uid":136662,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T09:10:04.000Z","msg":"我都試過認真呼吸<br />\n慢慢有d光包圍我<br />\n再練多排無啦啦身後面多咗個人影<br />\n時間仲可以停止<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b96f2d23b389a3a4c0be003432b977dff2c56b3","tid":749702,"uid":195396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4407d29ce93db9a5550f9097b5a89f108c69771b","tid":749702,"uid":62373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T09:09:42.000Z","msg":"呢句真呀<br />\n呼吸閉左 自己都唔知<br />\n之後先慢慢提自己 先正常返"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T09:11:34.000Z","msg":"我發覺我呀媽同我都係咁 我呀媽平時壓力都幾大 我諗有啲關係<br />\n<br />\n巴打放鬆啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec04e5e51f6755847d155161005795e497a4df5b","tid":749702,"uid":18048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"202d1ac92a9a3e5e90617b85c7a57b2505cee88e","tid":749702,"uid":136662,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T09:10:04.000Z","msg":"我都試過認真呼吸<br />\n慢慢有d光包圍我<br />\n再練多排無啦啦身後面多咗個人影<br 